<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ The Russian economy is reported to be <a href="//www.businessinsider.com/r-russian-economy-grinding-to-a-halt-as-ukraine-crisis-takes-heavy-toll-2014-24">grinding to a halt</a> as the Ukraine crisis takes a heavy toll.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ This is a story of five small businesses <a href="//globalvoicesonline.org/2014/03/24/5-small-businesses-run-by-rural-uruguan-women/">run by</a> rural Uruguayan women.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Wealthy Cubans are flaunting their cash, possibly a sign of <a href="//latino.foxnews.com/latino/lifestyle/2014/03/24/new-sign-cuba-moving-toward-capitalism-wealthy-cubans-are-flaunting-their-cash/">Cuba moving toward</a> capitalism.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A New Zealand banker explains howÂ <a href="//www.nzherald.co.nz/business/news/article.cfm?c_id=3&amp;objectid=11225322">local banks are assisting</a> small businesses after a devastating earthquake.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Technology</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Basecamp, maker of project management software, <a href="//techcrunch.com/2014/03/24/basecamp-becomes-latest-victim-of-ddos-attackers-attempting-to-extort-money-from-tech-companies/">was hit with</a> a distributed denial-of-service attack rendering its services temporarily unavailable.</p>
